@startuml AssignmentSubmissionWorkflow
title Assignment Submission Workflow (SMD-04)
hide empty description

' Color Customization
skinparam {
    BackgroundColor white
    ArrowColor #4C5FD5
    
    ' State Diagram specific
    StateBackgroundColor white
    StateBorderColor #4C5FD5
    StateStartColor #4C5FD5
    StateEndColor #4C5FD5
    
    ' Notes
    NoteBackgroundColor #FBBF24
    NoteBorderColor #FBBF24
}


state "New (Not Started)" as new_not_started
note right of new_not_started
No files have been uploaded, and no text 
has been entered. 
end note

state "Draft" as draft
note right of draft
The student has uploaded a file or saved 
text, but has not clicked the "Submit" 
button. The student can still modify the 
work. 
end note

state "Submitted" as submitted
note right of submitted
The student has finalized the submission 
before the Due Date. The content is 
locked from further editing. 
end note

state "Late Submitted" as late_submitted
note right of late_submitted
The student finalized the submission 
after the Due Date (only valid if the 
"Cut-off Date" has not passed). 
end note

state "Grading in Progress" as grading_in_progress
note right of grading_in_progress
The Instructor has opened the submission 
for review but hasn't finalized the 
score. 
end note

state "Graded/Released" as graded_released
note right of graded_released
The Instructor has assigned a score and 
feedback. The student receives a 
notification. 
end note

new_not_started --> draft : Upload File / Save Text
draft --> draft : Update File
draft --> late_submitted : Click Submit (Time < Due Date)
draft --> late_submitted : Click Submit (Time > Due Date)
late_submitted --> draft : Instructor Unlocks Submission
late_submitted --> grading_in_progress : Instructor Opens Grading Interface
grading_in_progress --> graded_released : Save Grade

@enduml
